      </div>

      <div class="pursuit text" id="pursuittext">
	<p class="pursuit content" id="pursuitcontent">Life is a chase. The universe contains infinite knowledge and possibilities, and though it is impossible to contain all that into  human brain, we try to accomplish all that we can. We try to make sense of life within our own limited time, set our goals, and hope to achieve our higher self by the end. This is my belief for a higher truth, and a pursuit of self fulfillment.</p>
