      <div id="inspiration" class="inspiration subject">
	<h1 class="title">Find your inspiration</h1>
      </div>
       <div class="inspire text" id="inspiretext">
	<p class="inspire content" id="inspirecontent">Inspiration comes in many forms and sizes; the lightest of words could create the heaviest effects. The desire to create change, improve life, end suffering, and anything else far wide and in between, is all a consequence of experiecing or viewing the experience of a situation where a change would modify a situation for the better. Thus, a primary importance of inspiration is that exposure is unlimited, much further reaching than ignorance.</p>
